snippet.title: Return to PopoloCrois: A STORY OF SEASONS Fairytale Launch Trailer (EU)
snippet.description:
Return to PopoloCrois: A STORY OF SEASONS Fairytale, the anticipated RPG/Farming simulator hybrid for Nintendo 3DS™,  is out NOW in Europe, Australia and New Zealand! Visit Nintendo eShop to download it!

For more information about this title, please check our website at www.marvelousgames.com.

©2016 Marvelous Europe Limited
